\c 13
\s Umfanekiso webhanti lelembu
\p
\v 1 Itsho njalo IN\nd kosi\nd* kimi: Hamba uzithengele ibhanti lelembu\x + Eks. 28.39. Levi 16.4.\x* elicolekileyo,\x + Seb. 21.11.\x* ulifake ekhalweni lwakho, ungalifaki emanzini.
\v 2 Ngasengithenga ibhanti njengokwelizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*, ngalifaka ekhalweni lwami.\x + 19.1; 27.2. Isa. 20.2. Hez. 4.1,2,3,4,5; 5.1,2,3,4; 12.3,4,5,6,7,8,9,10,11; 24.3,4,5.\x*
\v 3 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* laselifika kimi ngokwesibili lisithi:
\v 4 Thatha ibhanti olithengileyo elisokhalweni lwakho, usukume uye eYufrathi, ulifihle khona engoxweni yedwala.\x + 16.16. Isa. 7.19.\x*
\v 5 Ngasengihamba, ngalifihla ngaseYufrathi njengoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ingilayile.
\v 6 Kwasekusithi ekupheleni kwensuku ezinengi, iN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kimi: Sukuma, uye eYufrathi, u\add ye\add*thatha khona ibhanti engakulaya ukuthi ulifihle khona.
\v 7 Ngasengisiya eYufrathi, ngagebha, ngalithatha ibhanti endaweni lapho engangilifihle khona; khangela-ke, ibhanti lalonakele,\x + 13.9; 18.4.\x* lalingasasizi lutho.\x + 13.10. Hez. 15.4.\x*
\v 8 Laselifika kimi ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lisithi:
\v 9 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Ngalindlela\x + Hlab. 137.1.\x* ngizakonakalisa\x + 13.9; 18.4.\x* ukuziqhenya kukaJuda\x + Levi 26.19.\x* lokuziqhenya okukhulu kweJerusalema.
\v 10 Lababantu ababi, abala ukuzwa amazwi ami, abahamba ngobulukhuni benhliziyo yabo,\x + 3.17; 16.11,12.\x* belandela abanye onkulunkulu ukubakhonza, lokubakhothamela, bazakuba njengalelibhanti elingasizi lutho.\x + 13.10. Hez. 15.4.\x*
\v 11 Ngoba njengoba ibhanti linamathela okhalweni lomuntu, ngokunjalo nginamathelise kimi indlu yonke yakoIsrayeli lendlu yonke yakoJuda, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*; ukuze kimi babe ngabantu,\x + Eks. 19.5.\x* lebizo,\x + 33.9.\x*\x + Isa. 55.13.\x*\x + Zef. 3.20.\x* lendumiso,\x + 33.9.\x*\x + Zef. 3.20.\x*\x + Isa. 62.7.\x* lenkazimulo;\x + 33.9.\x* kodwa kabalalelanga.
\s Umfanekiso wezimbiza ezigcwaliswa ngewayini
\p
\v 12 Ngakho uzakhuluma kibo lelilizwi: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Yonke imbodlela\x + 48.12.\x* izagcwaliswa ngewayini.\x + 25.15.\x* Njalo bazakuthi kuwe:\x + Hez. 11.2,3.\x* Isibili kasikwazi yini ukuthi yonke imbodlela izagcwaliswa ngewayini?
\v 13 Ubususithi kibo: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Khangela, ngizagcwalisa bonke abakhileyo balelilizwe, lamakhosi ahlala esihlalweni sobukhosi sikaDavida,\x + 2.26; 17.19,20; 18.18; 19.3; 22.2.\x* labapristi,\x + 2.26; 17.19,20; 18.18; 19.3; 22.2.\x* labaprofethi,\x + 2.26; 17.19,20; 18.18; 19.3; 22.2.\x* labo bonke abahlali beJerusalema, ngokudakwa.\x + Hez. 23.33.\x*
\v 14 Njalo ngizabaphahlaza omunye komunye,\x + 19.11. Hlab. 2.9.\x* laboyise lamadodana ndawonye, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*; kangiyikuhawukela, kangiyikuyekela, kangiyikuba lomusa, ukuthi ngingabachithi.
\s AbakoJuda bazathunjwa ngenxa yokungaphenduki kwabo
\p
\v 15 Zwanini, libeke indlebe, lingaziqhenyi, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ikhulumile.
\v 16 Inikeni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu udumo,\x + Josh. 7.19.\x* ingakalethi ubumnyama,\x + 23.12. Amos 5.8; 8.9. Hlab. 139.12. Isa. 5.30; 8.22. Dute. 28.29. Joha. 11.10; 12.35.\x* lenyawo zenu zingakakhubeki ezintabeni zokuhwalala, lisalindela ukukhanya,\x + Isa. 59.9.\x* ikwenze kube lithunzi lokufa,\x + 2.6. Jobe 3.5.\x* ikwenze kube ngumnyama onzima.\x + Isa. 60.2.\x*
\v 17 Kodwa uba lingalaleli, umphefumulo wami uzakhala inyembezi endaweni zensitha ngenxa yokuziqhenya \add kwenu\add*,\x + Jobe 33.17.\x* lelihlo lami lizakhala inyembezi kabuhlungu,\x + 9.1.\x* lehlise inyembezi, ngoba umhlambi weN\nd kosi\nd* uthunjiwe.
\p
\v 18 Tshono enkosini\x + 2.26. 2 Kho. 24.12.\x* lendlovukazini\x + 2.26. 2 Kho. 24.12.\x*\x + 1 Kho. 11.19.\x* \add uthi\add*: Zithobeni, hlalani phansi; ngoba imiqhele yenu izawela phansi, umqhele wodumo lwenu.\x + Zaga 4.9; 16.31. Isa. 28.5; 62.3. Lilo 5.16.\x*
\v 19 Imizi yeningizimu izavalwa,\x + Josh. 6.1.\x* njalo kakho oza\add yi\add*vula; uJuda uzathunjwa, yena wonke, uzathunjwa ngokupheleleyo.
\v 20 Phakamisani amehlo enu, libone labo abavela enyakatho.\x + 1.13; 6.22.\x* Ungaphi umhlambi owaphiwa wona, umhlambi wakho omuhle?
\v 21 Uzakuthini uba esenza isijeziso phezu kwakho, ngoba wena ubafundise ukuthi \add babe\add* \add y\add*izinduna\x + Zek. 9.7; 12.5,6.\x* \add l\add*enhloko phezu kwakho;\x + Lilo 1.5.\x* inhlungu kaziyikukubamba yini njengowesifazana obelethayo?\x + 6.24.\x*
\p
\v 22 Njalo uba usithi enhliziyweni yakho: Kungani lezizinto zenzakele kimi?\x + 5.19.\x* Ngenxa yobunengi bobubi bakho amalogwe akho embuliwe,\x + 13.26. Nah. 3.5. Lilo 1.8. Isa. 3.17; 6.1.\x* \add l\add*ezithende zakho zaphathwa ngodlakela.
\v 23 UmEthiyophiya angasiphendula yini isikhumba sakhe, kumbe ingwe amabala ayo? \add Khona\add* lani lizakuba lakho ukwenza okuhle elejwayele ukwenza okubi.\x + Mat. 19.26.\x*
\v 24 Ngakho ngizabahlakaza njengamakhoba edluliswa ngomoya wenkangala.\x + Hlab. 1.4; 83.13.\x*
\v 25 Le yinkatho yakho, isabelo sezilinganiso zakho ezivela kimi,\x + Jobe 20.29. Hlab. 11.6.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, ngoba ungikhohliwe,\x + 2.32.\x* wathemba emangeni.\x + 10.14.\x*
\v 26 Ngakho lami ngizakwembula amalogwe akho phezu kobuso bakho,\x + 13.26. Nah. 3.5. Lilo 1.8. Isa. 3.17; 6.1.\x*\x + Hos. 2.10.\x* ukuze kubonakale ihlazo lakho.\x + Nah. 3.5.\x*
\v 27 Ngibonile ubufebe bakho, lokukhonya kwakho,\x + 5.8; 8.16.\x* inkohlakalo zokuphinga kwakho, phezu kwamaqaqa egangeni, amanyala akho.\x + 2.20.\x* Maye kuwe, Jerusalema! Kawuyikuhlambuluka yini?\x + Hez. 24.13.\x* Kusezadlula nini?